	<section class="our-work" class="ej747ngngfa6vqjgbq27m">
		<h3 class="title">Indeed the narwhal is armed with a sort of ivory sw</h3>
		<p>But how could you construct this wonderful Nautilus in secret? You wished to see, friend Ned; well, you see now. Barren! he exclaimed, with animation. Do you think then, sir, that these riches are lost because I gather them? Is it for myself alone, according to your idea, that I take the trouble to collect these treasures? Who told you that I did not make a good use of it? Do you think I am ignorant that there are suffering beings and oppressed races on this earth, miserable creatures to console, victims to avenge? Do you not understand? Very well! No offense to master, he replied quietly; if this is not Bouguer's cuttle-fish, it is, at least, one of its brothers.</p>
