	<section class="contact">
		<h3 class="o5garh0rh6lv58bbwv" class="title">A general cry arose from the frigate.</h3>	
		<p>Arrived at the robing-room, I saw that neither of my companions nor any of the ship's crew were to follow us on this excursion. Captain Nemo had not even proposed my taking with me either Ned or Conseil. Perfectly, Captain Nemo; but the air that you carry with you must soon be used; when it only contains fifteen per cent. of oxygen, it is no longer fit to breathe. But, said I, it is not a question of fishing for them with an iron swivel, hoisting them into the vessel, cutting off their tails with a blow of the chopper, ripping them up, and throwing their hearts into the sea! In any case, replied the Canadian, we shall be free, for we are floating.</p>
